_xResult.title: Leather and Lace Dress
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made cotton and wool knitted dress with leggings
_xResult.longdesc:
A dark red set is the perfect ensemble for the winter season. This custom made red dress is loose and long-sleeved, made out of a cotton and wool knit that will be sure to keep you warm. The trim on the bottom hemline and sleeves add a gorgeous detail and the leather is vegan and cruelty free. The leggings match the dark red of the top and are great for super chilly days that call for covered legs.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
